{"type":"message","id":"82551353","parentId":"155ecf20","timestamp":"2026-03-23T23:39:00.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Webhook is set correctly. The bot info confirms it's @BotShoppeBot (Bot Shoppe). The webhook URL is set to the new cloudflared quick tunnel URL.\n\nThe `last_synchronization_error_date` of 1773807500 corresponds to a Unix timestamp - let me check what that is. Actually, that doesn't matter much - it could be from a previous attempt.\n\nThe important things:\n1. ✅ Webhook is set to `https://dosage-permitted-sewing-commonly.trycloudflare.com`\n2. ✅ pending_update_count is 0 (no pending updates)\n3. ✅ @BotShoppeBot is confirmed as the bot name\n\n\n4. ✅ @hedgehogclawbot wasn't touched\n\nNow I need to update TOOLS.md with the new URL since the cloudflared tunnel URL changes on each restart.","thinkingSignature":"7628f10661881cc21d1c331283fc21a02bd0e41badcaf53872833c38dea899cd"},{"type":"text","text":"Webhook is live. Now updating TOOLS.md with the new URL:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dw89k0mfzq6b_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md","oldText":"## Telegram Webhook\n- **Status:** Webhook active (as of 2026-03-22 night)\n- **Tunnel:** cloudflared quick tunnel → `https://medication-ext-drinks-tri.trycloudflare.com`","newText":"## Telegram Webhook\n- **Status:** Webhook active (as of 2026-03-23)\n- **Tunnel:** cloudflared quick tunnel → `https://dosage-permitted-sewing-commonly.trycloudflare.com`"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4209,"output":344,"cacheRead":9991,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14544,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774309132526}}
