{"type":"message","id":"b58cd048","parentId":"9042f573","timestamp":"2026-03-23T23:39:07.275Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_hlvhu3bnojry_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\TOOLS.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n 67 - **Status:** Webhook active (as of 2026-03-23)\n 68 - **Tunnel:** cloudflared quick tunnel → `https://dosage-permitted-sewing-commonly.trycloudflare.com`\n 69 - **Bot token:** `8587631426:AAHvqmo--g25LqsClCWCXj4m617cn2v7V7Q`\n 70 - **⚠️ Limitation:** Quick tunnels get a NEW URL each time cloudflared restarts\n-71   - If tunnel drops → manually re-register: `Invoke-RestMethod \"https://api.telegram.org/bot<token>/setWebhook?url=<new_url>\"`\n-72   - To find current URL: check cloudflared session log (session `keen-lobster`)\n+71   - If tunnel drops → manually re-register using this script: `restart-tunnel.ps1` in workspace\n+72   - To find current URL: check the cloudflared process output (last session name: `plaid-kelp`)\n 73 - **Cloudflared path:** `C:\\Program Files (x86)\\cloudflared\\cloudflared.exe`\n 74 - **Persistent setup (not done):** Named Cloudflare tunnel + domain = static URL","firstChangedLine":71},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774309147237}}
{"type":"message","id":"34de5d6a","parentId":"b58cd048","timestamp":"2026-03-23T23:39:16.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me also save a quick restart script so future me can easily restart the tunnel and get the URL.","thinkingSignature":"72168c1002c871cfa788f1c5e2c874f74dda55ee5c55f0961fd64172378b7165"},{"type":"text","text":"\nNow let me create a restart script for easier future recovery:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gor0gvec3hl3_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\restart-tunnel.ps1","content":"# Telegram Bot Webhook Tunnel Restart Script\n# Usage: .\\restart-tunnel.ps1\n# This script restarts the cloudflared quick tunnel and re-registers the Telegram webhook.\n\n$BOT_TOKEN = \"8587631426:AAHvqmo--g25LqsClCWCXj4m617cn2v7V7Q\"\n$LOCAL_PORT = 8080\n$URL_FILE = \"$env:TEMP\\cf_url.txt\"\n\n# Kill existing cloudflared processes\nGet-Process cloudflared -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 2\n\n# Start new quick tunnel\nWrite-Host \"Starting cloudflared quick tunnel...\"\n$proc = Start-Process \"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\cloudflared\\cloudflared.exe\" `\n    -ArgumentList \"tunnel\",\"--url\",\"http://localhost:$LOCAL_PORT\" `\n    -NoNewWindow -PassThru -RedirectStandardOutput $URL_FILE\n\n# Wait for URL to appear\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 8\n\nif (Test-Path $URL_FILE) {\n    $output = Get-Content $URL_FILE\n    $urlLine = $output | Where-Object { $_ -match \"https://.*trycloudflare\\.com\" }\n    if ($urlLine -match \"(https://[^ ]+)\" ) {\n        $TUNNEL_URL = $matches[1]\n        Write-Host \"Tunnel URL: $TUNNEL_URL\"\n        \n        # Set webhook\n        Write-Host \"Setting Telegram webhook...\"\n        $response = Invoke-RestMethod \"https://api.telegram.org/bot$BOT_TOKEN/setWebhook?url=$TUNNEL_URL\"\n        if ($response.ok) {\n            Write-Host \"Webhook set successfully!\"\n        } else {\n            Write-Host \"Webhook set failed: $($response.description)\"\n        }\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"Failed to capture tunnel URL\"\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4847,"output":485,"cacheRead":9991,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15323,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774309147277}}
